des:
Test your knowledge of Discraft and the disc industry. With this first quiz, we've got some easy birdies and some hard par 4s. Think you're up for the challenge? 

Note: While playing the quiz, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next question. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the quiz.
